---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Commercial Decorating in Middlesex & the Home Counties | Hancock' description='Professional commercial decorating across Middlesex and the Home Counties. Fixed-price quotes, City & Guilds certified, no subcontractors.' activePage='services'>
<section style="position:relative;height:420px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(8).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 35%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 56px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/services" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Services</a> / Commercial Decorating</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,56px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Commercial Decorating</h1>
    <p style="font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;max-width:520px;line-height:1.5;">Offices, rental properties, and commercial spaces across Middlesex. Deadlines met. Tenants respected.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Who this is for</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Property managers, landlords, and facility teams across the Home Counties.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">Commercial decorating has different demands from domestic work. You have handover dates, tenants who can't be displaced unnecessarily, finishes that need to last under high traffic, and a budget that needs to be known upfront and not revised.</p>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">We work in offices, rental flats and houses, common parts of managed buildings, and commercial premises. If the job runs over multiple phases, we can plan around your schedule.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">How we work</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">8am starts. Work around your timeline. Fixed price.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">We can start at 8am and, where required, work outside standard hours to minimise disruption to occupied spaces. The quote covers the full scope. If conditions on site require a change to that scope, we discuss it before proceeding — never after.</p>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">We cover Uxbridge, Watford, Bracknell, and the business corridors of the M25/M4. Contact us to discuss your project and timeline.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:64px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,40px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Discuss your commercial project.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 36px;">Fixed price. Documented scope. Timeline agreed before start.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
